line_1: Why should I then the Heav'nly spark controul,
line_2: Since there's no brighter Ray in all my Soul,

line_1: While languishing she mourned in folly's sad control.
line_2: By which hope led the wandering cheated soul;

line_1: If once indulg'd, it never brooks controul;
line_2: Beware of passion, it unmans the soul,
